{"tid":1575774,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「港人質素」抄不到 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T03:25:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce21f727be42cefbdd4e95badcf6f5e5ae6aad62","tid":1575774,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190917/20769351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F20769351&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86raDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=3d350ca0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190917%2F20769351&h=16582e1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190917/20769351</a><br />\n<br />\n「港人質素」抄不到 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190917/large/1568622909_41a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190917%2Flarge%2F1568622909_41a5.jpg&h=33514963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不管無能又橫蠻的港府發反對或不反對通知書，香港人仍堅持在915「國際民主日」遊行示威，響應聯合國理念，努力爭取自由人權文明的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n從金鐘法院道的英國駐港領事館，到銅鑼灣、灣仔、金鐘、中環&hellip;&hellip;同以前數度大遊行一樣的「自由行」路線，一樣的人潮，一樣的民心──而且不像那些「愛國愛黨」人士般，有錢收。<br />\n<br />\n淪落中的香港，要多少年才能恢復幾成舊觀，才可救回殘命？不知道也無法推測，盡力而為。心腸歹毒的林鄭，為一己之私，戀棧權位，把香港破壞成如此不堪，死傷無數，實在不值！必要光復，這是最堅定的信念。<br />\n<br />\n台北朋友有參加西門町的支援港人大合唱行動。問候我們這些受過期山埃催淚彈（二千多枚）影響，久咳不癒的難民。台友道，港人合唱自創的《願榮光歸香港》，那些大叔大媽又收錢賣唱國歌來對抗。我們笑，不止呢，還有學人登獅子山舉五星紅旗（但騎呢地為「實行真雙普選」宣傳）、文宣海報、在外國報章登廣告、撐警集會遊行&hellip;&hellip;甚至無恥地改編港歌侵佔人家心血成果──總之跟人口水尾，不但無新意，還是庸劣山寨貨，那以「性天使」假片來蒙混新屋嶺女示威者遭黑警武警輪姦事件，更是居心叵測。<br />\n<br />\n不過任你肆意抄襲，只有一樣永遠抄不到，就是「港人的質素」。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n深深藍絲內心深處 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則"},{"pid":"8c079fc863533f47250d93be4e630389f3a7e582","tid":1575774,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f1d54e6dc7785fbd1631d9a524e6cabe670ca36","tid":1575774,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"還有學人登獅子山舉五星紅旗（但騎呢地為「實行真雙普選」宣傳）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190915/large/1568479093_915c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190915%2Flarge%2F1568479093_915c.gif&h=b06aa19a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}